COXA JOINT STANDARD (OBSIDIAN-8 V3)

Rotation Axis: Vertical (Yaw)
Load Type: Radial dominant + shock loads

SHAFT:
- Diameter: 8mm (minimum) → 10mm preferred
- Material: Hardened steel (or precision rod)
- Fit: Slip fit through bearings, clamped on output side

BEARINGS:
- Type: 608ZZ (8x22x7) OR 6000 series if upgrading
- Quantity: 2 per leg (top + bottom)
- Spacing: 20–35mm apart (CRITICAL for stability)

HOUSING:
- Fully captured bearing pockets
- Press fit tolerance: -0.02mm
- Reinforced outer walls (≥4mm thickness)

SERVO INTERFACE:
- Servo does NOT carry radial load
- Output drives shaft via:
    → Clamping hub OR
    → Steel coupler

LOAD PATH:
LEG → SHAFT → BEARINGS → HOUSING → 2020 FRAME

DO NOT:
- Mount servo directly as structural support
- Use single bearing
- Print shaft
